metadata.name: Rapid wr
metadata.description:
Film, analog multiexposure, 
digital scan, 2288x3395 px

In my photos of buildings, 
streets, malls I share my personal 
analysis and research. By finding key 
features of the architectural volume I create 
a new architectural objects that hover in the air and have a different interpretation in urban space. I often use the technique of symmetry and call it a 
variant of unwrapping (bending) perspective.
